Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.30,0:10:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now let this into your pussy. {lit: eat it with your coochie}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.09,0:10:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Vary it — gentle, strong, try different techniques so we can get an accurate reading. {of your vaginal pressure}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.17,0:10:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an essential check \Nfor making a quality clone.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.37,0:10:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do this, \Nyour wish won't come true. Got it?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.34,0:10:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Momoko totally can't \Nendure something like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.62,0:11:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoko... feels so lonely by herself. {?? w/e she means}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.51,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.13,0:11:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um, I'd like to make a request to the director...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the director, Kosumo Kaoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.78,0:11:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Is that so?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.03,0:11:44.95,Thought,,0,0,0,,This ain't matchin' the data Shiho gave us! \NDirector at such a young age? {kansai accent}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.95,0:11:47.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,Did he hand over management \Nto his daughter or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.47,0:11:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now take off your bottoms \Nand get on the examination table.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.23,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be surprised about, is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.29,0:11:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You came for an examination, right? \NOr is it something else?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.02,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,U-Um... No, you're right...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,Zowie... I forgot.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.87,0:12:06.10,Thought,,0,0,0,,I just casually came in as an outside patient, \Nbut this is the gynecology department, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.10,0:12:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? There's nothing to be embarrassed about between women, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.13,0:12:11.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, please take care of me.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.22,0:12:19.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.86,Thought,,0,0,0,,She is definitely super A-rank.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.48,Thought,,0,0,0,,I dunno why, but dis feels very weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.48,0:12:37.92,Thought,,0,0,0,,And the color is a beautiful salmon pink \Nthat matches her looks.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.92,0:12:40.51,Thought,,0,0,0,,The color, the shape — it's simply perfect!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.89,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Doctor, what are you...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.68,0:12:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't worry, I'm just checking your health.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.83,0:12:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.53,0:12:51.96,Thought,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, I'm startin' to enjoy it. {feel}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.96,0:12:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to give birth? \NIs that why you came in? {why she came to see the gynecologist}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.15,0:12:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... yes I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:56.13,0:13:00.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,If she keeps stirrin' it up like that, \NI really won't be able to hol' back.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.41,0:13:02.85,Thought,,0,0,0,,She's licking it! \NWhat the hell is her deal?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.46,0:13:09.89,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shit, I got carried away.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What da... It's a man!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.37,0:13:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What da hell are you doin'?!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.87,0:13:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap... I acted without thinkin'.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.00,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor? Doctor, what's wrong? Doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.36,0:13:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Benika.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.34,0:13:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiho?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with your outfit? {lit: what's that outfit - idk what's wrong with it, maybe that she has her panties in her hand and not on her?}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.56,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, \Nthe info ya gave us was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.67,0:13:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The director here ain't a 60-year-old ailin' old man, it's a young doctor!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's a total pervert \Nwho likes crossdressin'!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.89,0:13:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange. The doctor \Nshould be single with no family.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.42,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But he definitely introduced himself that way. I know what I heard. {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.82,0:14:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Leave the rest to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.34,0:14:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, we haven't heard from Momoko. Can you check on her?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.79,0:14:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You be careful too. \NAnd try not to catch a cold. {lit: if you stay like that, it's bad - guess it was about her outfit after all?}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Director.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:11.28,0:14:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Saionji, dispatched from the university hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I hadn't heard about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.92,0:14:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be. \NWe definitely received your request.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it was an oversight on my end?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.38,0:14:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We are short on staff, \Nso let's discuss it in the reception room.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.16,0:14:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.36,0:14:32.64,Thought,,0,0,0,,Another hottie. \NShe's totally my type.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.87,Thought,,0,0,0,,So this is the director Benika was talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.87,0:14:38.32,Thought,,0,0,0,,But with that voice and appearance, \Nhe doesn't look like a man at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.73,0:14:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:46.20,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been acquainted with your brilliant work for a while, Dr. Kosumo. {heard of since long ago}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially your research in cloning — \Nit's Nobel Prize level!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.91,0:14:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my father's research.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.40,0:15:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But given the strict views of today's society on ethics, it's not an easy field to work in.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.22,0:15:06.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's an adopted daughter or something{ after all}? \NThis is a major data oversight.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.54,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can't let my guard down with her. \NShe must be the authorities' spy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:11.54,0:15:13.60,Thought,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't born yesterday either! {lit: but don't underestimate me either}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.52,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,T-This black tea... {lit: in black tea}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.91,0:15:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Saionji-san?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.04,0:15:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... you're...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kosumo Kaoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.01,0:15:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The spelling is a bit different from the name \Nyou were asking about though. {I think he means the kanji, the lake-nest-algae thing from before }
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,A man?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.66,0:15:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a natural trait I was born with.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:33.05,0:15:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,With just one switch in my throat, \NI can be both a man and woman. {??? lit: enjoy together}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.63,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now who the hell are {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.71,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got good taste, don't you? {in underwear}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.80,0:15:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that nice? \NYou're getting me intrigued.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.18,0:15:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, n-no... stop. Please stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.82,0:15:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,No! D-Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.82,0:16:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a great view. Not bad at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.74,0:16:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you're getting wetter and wetter.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.42,0:16:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fantastic. \NAnd the smell is absolutely irresistible.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.88,0:16:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you... doing this to me...?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.94,0:16:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about time I enjoy myself too.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:35.77,0:16:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,That black tea had a sedative, \Nmixed in with an aphrodisiac in it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.97,0:16:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at how much you're burning up \Nand how hard you are sucking me in.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.91,0:16:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, who are you really? \NWhat's your goal?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.66,0:17:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. I'll enjoy you plenty first \Nbefore I dispose of you.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.99,0:17:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That felt great.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This could become addictive. {lit: looks like it'll become a habit}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:32.37,0:17:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't take it... \NMomoko feels like she's going to lose it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:37.96,0:17:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break... {/forgive me}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoko! The hell \Nare you doin' here all by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.86,0:17:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Miss Benika, \NMomoko was only following orders.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when doing the right thing, \Nyou're still Momoko, all right. {???????}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.32,0:18:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I thought if I didn't follow the orders exactly...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.96,0:18:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't... be able to...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,find out the truth about this hospital.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.80,0:18:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That was to be expected.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.22,0:18:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help me, Miss Benika!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.55,0:18:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The infiltration has only just begun.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.32,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For now you need to stay like this \Nand watch how the enemy moves.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.08,0:18:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.73,0:18:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,As bait, you have to endure it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.51,0:18:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a government spy.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.24,0:18:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been following my orders properly. Good girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shiho? So she messed up?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.41,0:18:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, then. \NNow we've got two new products in hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.62,0:18:54.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,Products?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.72,0:19:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well hello there, Dr. Kosumo Kaoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.72,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to a hint you gave me, \Nthe "clone" Dutch wife project is a success.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.19,0:19:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The cute girls who lost their memories \Nare a huge hit with the customers.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.10,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No one doubts they're only cloned humans.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.75,0:19:35.58,Thought,,0,0,0,,What the hell does that mean? \NSo the whole clonin' thing was a lie?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.58,0:19:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just what you deserve for abandoning me \Nin America as your illegitimate child.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.54,0:19:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than your mortal body, I took everything from you — your hospital and assets.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.35,0:19:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The nurses all think of me as your adopted child. \NNo one suspects a thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.47,0:19:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the sham is exposed, \NI'll just disappear.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the only one taking the fall. {lit: only you'll get arrested}
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.97,0:20:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you alive until then.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.47,0:20:02.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,What a calculating criminal. {??????? think she means he thought of everything?}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.47,0:20:04.45,Thought,,0,0,0,,Ah, so that's what it was.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.45,0:20:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, it's time to deliver \Na clone Dutch wife to a new customer.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you more later.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.61,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Just endure it while the customer has a taste. {????? lit: bear with it while letting the client have a taste - later it's revealed that while the customer is trying the girl kosumo knocks them out}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It only paralyzes the autonomic nerves.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.99,0:20:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I won't do something wasteful like selling my precious collection to customers.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.46,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I still need to thoroughly taste these new products myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.46,0:20:32.52,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shiho, Momoko, forgive me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.66,Thought,,0,0,0,,I can't rescue you right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.66,0:20:37.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,I need to catch this guy and his full \Ncriminal operation red-handed. {????????}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.82,0:20:38.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,Hang in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.31,0:20:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Red to Black. {apparently the codename of that guy in the office}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.89,0:20:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Red to Black!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.91,0:20:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? \NPick up faster, you idiot!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.27,0:20:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Black. \NRed's message is acknowledged.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:49.78,0:20:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop tailing and infiltrate Room 501 at the Marine Resort.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.69,0:20:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying so casually?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.83,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiho and Momoko are about to get fucked \Nby some perverted customer!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.15,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't panic Red. \NThe customer for this one is me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.48,0:21:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I slipped into the customer list \Nthrough a secret route. It's me.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.40,0:21:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk. Why didn't you say that sooner?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:26.60,0:21:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the conductor, Kuroyanagi-san, correct? \NIt's an honor to meet you. {is this a reference to https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E9%BB%92%E6%9F%B3%E5%AE%88%E7%B6%B1 ? dawg... also his codename is black and kuro means black}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.99,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:32.20,0:21:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I've passed the strict screening.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We thoroughly checked your background.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.68,0:21:40.65,Thought,,0,0,0,,Our data forgery was perfect.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.65,0:21:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you like what you see. {??????}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.78,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the membership fee.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.24,0:21:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.85,0:21:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, as per the rules, \Nplease choose one of the two.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.87,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a cooling-off system, so even after use, \Nyou can return it if you're not satisfied.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:56.10,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's surprisingly reasonable. {/honest}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.28,0:22:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our company motto is clean business.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.55,0:22:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try with the mouth first?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Or from here?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.82,0:22:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.44,0:22:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to do with someone watching.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:14.96,0:22:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:16.40,0:22:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The rules state that the first trial \Nmust be done with me present.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.96,0:22:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood. Can't be helped.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a look inside first.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.06,0:22:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.84,0:22:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This freak bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.75,0:22:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.19,0:22:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You... {maybe a beginning of "when did you"}
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.31,0:22:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. More importantly, \Nhelp Violet and Pink.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.57,0:22:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know the full scope of his scheme.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.56,0:22:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was pretending to sell clone Dutch wives
Dialogue: 10,0:22:59.55,0:23:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,while actually providing real girls \Nwith paralyzed autonomic nerves.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.03,0:23:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Unforgivable.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.26,0:23:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san was in danger too. {that's black/kuroyanagi; she means when kosumo was about to knock him on the head}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:07.04,0:23:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,His method is to knock out unsuspecting customers while they're distracted
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.89,0:23:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with a blunt weapon \Nand steal their membership fees.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:13.50,0:23:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he'd keep the girls as part \Nof his own collection for enjoyment.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.44,0:23:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all gain and no loss.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.96,0:23:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I recorded that whole conversation with a hidden camera as evidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.03,0:23:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way he'd go into hiding \Nwithout his precious collection. {/run away and leave ... behind}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.82,0:23:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how criminals think.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.50,0:23:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyuu{meaningless amazement sfx}! Kuroki-san is so smart!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:30.28,0:23:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You dupe! Stop acting all innocent \Nevery single time! {natural airhead}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:33.00,0:23:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give Momoko a massage later!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.73,0:23:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... That's enough already!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:51.00,0:23:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.71,0:23:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is as far as you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:55.37,0:23:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you underestimate the police, \Nyou'll get burned! {??????? only hear "underestimate", maybe the police?}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:06.93,0:24:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves you right! {????????? not a clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:08.45,0:24:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because crime never pays! {????????????? fucking same; is this even japanese???}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:10.26,0:24:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're under arrest for confinement, \Nasset seizure, and drug misuse.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:18.58,0:24:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, that ain't not feelin' resolved at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:21.27,0:24:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Momoko feels the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:23.50,0:24:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Kuroki-san, you were planning to have a little taste of Shiho and Momoko while you were at it, weren't you?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:28.88,0:24:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't say nonsense!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:30.93,0:24:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your superior, you know. \NPlus, I'm a public servant of the state.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:35.24,0:24:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.81,0:24:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. After going that far, it won't feel resolved unless you properly follow through.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.34,0:24:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! The hell're you saying, you brat!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.20,0:24:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But what can I do? Momoko is still tingling all over and it feels so incomplete.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:52.13,0:24:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, you two.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:54.64,0:24:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Are you standing up for Kuroki-san now? \NAfter all that was done to you? {/defending}
Dialogue: 10,0:24:59.36,0:25:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like we'll have to look further into exactly how far our special mission duties extend. {meaning getting drugged and almost sold wasn't among their duties}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:04.32,0:25:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah yeah, better to make it clear right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:07.71,0:25:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Miss Benika...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:09.99,0:25:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Please soothe this burning body of Momoko's!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:12.91,0:25:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Momoko, stop gropin' my tits!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:15.27,0:25:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:16.10,0:25:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care for your pleadin' anymore! {??????? probably}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:17.78,0:25:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're making me feel weird too.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:19.47,0:25:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But Miss Benika...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:20.52,0:25:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Don't come near me, that's gross!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:22.34,0:25:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... {konna?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:23.41,0:25:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to not touch me there, so stop! Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.38,0:25:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiho, do something about this girl!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:29.16,0:25:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Benika!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:36.73,0:25:40.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And so the case reached a resolution.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.23,0:25:44.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The women were rescued and, \Nalong with the doctor, received treatment
Dialogue: 10,0:25:44.94,0:25:47.57,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and are recovering through rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.57,0:25:52.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The culprit Kosumo Kaoru couldn't be formally prosecuted due to a lack of official family registration, {??????? I'm guessing that means he has no documents and was living illegally?}
Dialogue: 10,0:25:52.84,0:25:56.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,but has been given a lifelong position \Nat the Police Science Research Institute
Dialogue: 10,0:25:56.51,0:26:00.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and given an honest path forward as a woman. {?????? is that supposed to be punishment only because he can't change his job? also is he a man or did he just just switch his organs too, not just his voice, with a flick of his throat??? I feel like even the creators didn't bother answering any of that so there's no point asking, or I'm hearing all this terribly wrong, but that's also their fault for coming up with such impenetrable bullshit}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.59,0:26:08.51,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The special investigation team Love Love Police \Nsets out once again today for bold undercover missions.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:09.13,0:26:12.47,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No matter what seductive traps await them,
Dialogue: 10,0:26:12.47,0:26:16.93,Narrator,,0,0,0,,or what mortal dangers lie ahead, \Nthey are not allowed to falter.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:18.06,0:26:24.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Challenging unforgivable injustice and evil, \Nwhich way is tomorrow for the Love Love Police? {ashita no joe reference, every NEP there ended with "ashita wa docchi da"}
Dialogue: 10,0:26:43.54,0:26:53.69,Song,,0,0,0,,{Watashi wa Love2 Police by... 西園寺紫穂? anyway, obviously no lyrics or aanything on the web, translating by ear} In the twilight town, the darkness approaches, and the night takes over
Dialogue: 10,0:26:56.14,0:27:08.76,Song,,0,0,0,,A silent lonely message echoes in my chest
Dialogue: 10,0:27:08.76,0:27:19.62,Song,,0,0,0,,Even with a battered body and soul, \NI have to keep going
Dialogue: 10,0:27:21.54,0:27:33.54,Song,,0,0,0,,My love is starting now because he's all my destiny
Dialogue: 10,0:27:33.54,0:27:39.14,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't stare at me, I am Love Love Police! Police!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.48,0:27:45.02,Song,,0,0,0,,Even knowing what I want is your heart
Dialogue: 10,0:27:46.06,0:27:52.54,Song,,0,0,0,,Don't look away, I am Love Love Police! Police!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:53.11,0:28:02.71,Song,,0,0,0,,What gets wet isn't just my eyes \NNothing can stop me, I shall get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.71,0:28:05.71,Song,,0,0,0,,
